title: An Interview with Clifford Brown, Jr.

description:
In this interview from 2008, Clifford Brown, Jr. discusses growing up the son of a jazz legend. This is an outtake from the video documentary BROWNIE SPEAKS. 
Director: Don Glanden
Editor: Brad Glanden
